{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 1a presents a photograph of the structure.",
    "LUMO is equipped with 18 uni-axial accelerometers located across 9 measurement levels (ML), that measure its orthogonal deflection and the horizontal motion.",
    "Pairs of accelerometers are placed at each ML in the x-and y-directions.",
    "At the 10th measurement level (ML10), three strain gauges (one on each of the three legs) and a thermocouple also measure the strain and the temperature of the structure, respectively.",
    "At six locations throughout the structure, controlled damage states can be introduced using reversible damage mechanisms."
  ]
}